text: Mojmír Stuchlík (30 June 1930 - 10 September 2016)Semilský sport se loučí s prvním olympionikem Mojmírem Stuchlíkem at Naše Pojizeří portal, 19 September 2016. was a Czech ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:People from Semily
